languages.text: "Но не мы. Наши нити переплетены навечно, Домин'{name}, ибо мою службу тебе прервет лишь Неумирающий".
"But not you and I, Domin'{name}. Our threads cannot be unwoven, and only the Undying One will end my service to you."

languages.text: «Pero eso no nos ocurrirá a nosotros, Domin'{name}. Las hebras de nuestro destino ya no pueden desligarse, y solo el Inmortal puede poner fin al servicio que le presto».

languages.original_text: "But not you and I, Domin'{name}. Our threads cannot be unwoven, and only the Undying One will end my service to you."

languages.text: “但你我二人的丝线却并非如此，秘者{name}。我们的丝线无法分开，只有不死之神才能结束我对你的侍奉。”
languages.original_text: "But not you and I, Domin'{name}. Our threads cannot be unwoven, and only the Undying One will end my service to you."
